high_descs: Turn left and take a step then turn left and walk to the table.
Pick up the box of tissues that are in front of you on the table.
Turn left and walk all the way to the coffee table beyond the chair then turn right to face the middle of it.
Put the tissues on the coffee table close to the laptop to it's left.
Turn right and walk past the chair then take two steps left and walk to the table.
Pickup the box of tissues closest to you on the table.
Walk back to where you put the first box of tissues.
Put this box to the left of the first box of tissues you put on the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Put two boxes of tissues on the table.

high_descs: Turn around and go forward to the side of the wooden dining table.
Pick up the box of tissue on the table near the front.
Turn left and go to the middle of the coffee table on the right.
Place the box of tissues on the table on the left of the lap top.
Turn right and go to the side of the dining table facing the living room.
Pick up the box of tissues near the front.
Turn around and go around the arm chairs back to the coffee table.
Place the box of tissues on the left of the first box.
anns.task_desc: Move two boxes of tissues to the coffee table.

high_descs: Turn around and face the table where the tissue box is.
Pick the tissue box up from the table.
Go left and then turn right to face the table with the computer on it.
Put the tissue box down on the table.
Go right and then left and turn to the right to face the table with the statue on it.
Pick the tissue box on the right up from the table.
Turn to the right and then go right again and turn to face the table.
Put the box of tissue on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put two boxes of tissue on a table.
